{"tid":1490057,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「長文」何謂勇武?何謂和理非?","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T15:36:27.000Z","uid":52711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9a6a39352d97bae13e73e2d8e8fb0589e1a125","tid":1490057,"uid":52711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"首先醜話講在前，我係想引發討論，唔係想強加自己既想法俾大家。而我亦唔係咩大智慧，只係區區一介垃圾ive仔，想喺到口出狂言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，僅僅如此，還望大家見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源係睇到以下呢個post :<br />\n<br />\n[細思極恐] 懷疑中共策劃緊另一場陰謀，已經成功瓦解緊成場運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486236</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當中o既「<span style=\"color: red;\">目的一：進一步分化「和理非」同「勇武派」，等香港人自己打自己人！</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n因為真係已經睇到有實質性既分化現象，例如「<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果乜乜乜 我地割唔割?</span>」「<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非滿意未？</span>」。或者佢地冇惡意，但 其實係<span style=\"color: brown;\">潛意識o既慢性分化</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我個人認為好危險亦正中共匪下懷。好似以下呢幅圖其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已經</span>係<span style=\"color: red;\">一個小小既警號</span>:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijjiXR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijjiXR4.jpg&h=5d85a6d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有見及此，令我不得不重新審視勇同和理非既關係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />目前主流既共識不外乎「前線交俾勇武」「遊行文宣嗌口號交俾和理非」。我沉思左成日，可能大家認為咁就係be water各有各爬山，或者重新睇返李小龍句說話:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Empty your mind,                                            清空你的思想，不要限制自己的框框，<br />\nbe formless, shapeless, like water.                  水無形無相，<br />\nPut water into a cup. Becomes the cup.          倒進杯子，它就是杯<br />\nPut water into a teapot. Becomes the teapot.  倒進茶壺，它就是茶壺。<br />\nWater can flow or creep or drip or crash.         水能奔流、能緩行、能滴濺、亦能衝擊。<br />\nBe water my friend.</span></blockquote><br />\n</span><br />\n我認為連日來各位手足o既行動已經做到o左水倒喺咩容器，就會變成咩形狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但完全忽視左Empty your mind,be formless, shapeless, like water.到底何謂水 ? 被和理非同勇武之概念框死哂。我想喺到大膽打破大家既固有想法或者指出大家忽略左既重點。就係:<br />\n我地各位手足喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有道德、有道義、有法治、有公義</span></span>既土地上出生，且孕育於此地，本應<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民皆為和理非</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n遇到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不道德、不道義、不法治、不公義</span></span>之諸事，理應<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民幻化為勇武</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！不分「<span style=\"color: violet;\">和</span>」「<span style=\"color: pink;\">勇</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有遇見不公且挺身站出黎既有良知之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">人</span></span>，出生為人理應如此，此亦稱作「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人性</span></span>」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者可以引用以下例子增加我o既說服力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32LNRxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32LNRxU.jpg&h=bf278f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中穿藍衣的白髮婆婆，佢o既形象喺我打呢篇文o既時候一直喺我腦海中浮現<br />\n<blockquote>示威者與警察一直陷入對峙，期間一名穿淺藍色上衣，拄拐杖的白髮婆婆突然衝出來，向前線示威者哭訴：「你哋走啦！你哋快啲走啦！」並「大」字型張開四肢，擋在示威者前面，多名年輕示威者拉着她，一名女示威者更直接攬着藍衣婆婆的腰。<br />\n<br />\n示威者不斷勸婆婆離開現場，惟婆婆堅持他們不走她也不走。示威者為使婆婆離開，於是說：「得，你走我哋走！」並開始向後退，藍衣婆婆見狀方跟着一起後退</blockquote><br />\n佢當時o既行為比任何前線更為勇武：企係賤畜與前線之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但思想更任何人更為和理非：叫前線唔好有衝突，唔想你地受傷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就說明我地更加唔應該分「<span style=\"color: violet;\">和</span>」「<span style=\"color: pink;\">勇</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 還望可以成為大家既新共識：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民皆為和理非，全民皆可化勇武。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後有一個偏離主題既小小問題亦有一定爆炸性既提議想問一問連仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連仔一直以來都會聽會員既提議亦都一直有做改進，好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但係基本上都係面向會員，就冇乜策略係面向<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">非會員</span></span>，我相信非會員既數目絕對有會員既好幾倍。唔理係mon post狗又好一般和理非上黎睇post既又好，佢地入到黎對連登既訊息都係照單全收，咁就好容易比3毛風向狗帶動，造成不必要既分化。咁我就想喺到問如果可以比<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非會員封鎖權限</span></span>，你覺得點？可以係註冊一個臨時ac/唔洗註冊ac之類既做法。只給予單一權限：封鎖。正正係全民需要但唔會影響會員日常既重要功能。我唔太熟呢方面，淨係想問可行性/成效以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">達致全民向3毛say no!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a5092c52eb86acfdaa42e43406c7114b2fbaff","tid":1490057,"uid":52711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b66a00890a5fa9172f8ef3c4804d2d4362ad66","tid":1490057,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1451cc79fd553c3ee97fb9cf6218ad9f0c45ff2f","tid":1490057,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cda98a3f773ef2bc6575e7212523ddcffd8d955","tid":1490057,"uid":52711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54e3cfbb0145de5f65443c137914be93e74356b5","tid":1490057,"uid":52711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a685014de5c61d68dfac0f6dcb875257f7317b","tid":1490057,"uid":52711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}